<!--
  Template: Order Bump with Future Discount
  File: 02-order-bump-discount.mjml
  Category: upsell / cross-sell
  
  Purpose:
  Encourage customers to add one more item to their existing order before checkout.
  Incentivize with 20% off next purchase as a reward for upgrading current order.
  
  When to send:
  - Post-purchase (within 2-4 hours after order confirmation)
  - Before order is shipped/processed
  - Cart abandonment recovery (alternative use case)
  - After first purchase (new customer upsell)
  
  Personalize:
  - {{first_name}}
  - {{order_number}} (optional reference)
  - {{discount_code}} for 20% off next order
  - "Add to my order" link → modify existing order or recommended products
  - Product recommendations based on purchase history
  - Brand logo + colors (#1B4332 primary, #f8f5ef background)
    
  Notes:
  - Marketing email (requires unsubscribe link - included in footer)
  - Soft upsell approach: "caring" tone vs aggressive sales
  - Educational section "How it Works" reduces friction
  - Navigation bar keeps brand touchpoints alive (Trending, Body, Face, etc.)
  - Works well for beauty/wellness brands with community-driven messaging
  - Time-sensitive: only valid while order is still modifiable (24-48h window)
  - A/B test: discount now vs. discount next time
  
  Conversion goal:
  Primary: Increase Average Order Value (AOV) by 15-30%
  Secondary: Build loyalty with future discount incentive
  Tertiary: Drive product discovery through "Discover more" CTA
-->
